title: House Democrat Nydia Velazquez Diagnosed with 'Presumed Coronavirus Infection'
description: Rep. Nydia Velazquez (D-NY) has been diagnosed with a "presumed coronavirus infection," she announced on Monday.
content:
Rep. Nydia Velazquez (D-NY) has been diagnosed with a “presumed coronavirus infection,” she announced on Monday.
